Sida ku xusan daabacaadda toddobaad (3 Maarso 2020), si loo xaqiijiyo kiiska la tuhunsan yahay, falanqayn dhammaystiran ayaa loo baahan yahay in la isku daro hal shay oo taariikhda cudur-darrada ah laba shay oo muujinta cudur-darrada ah, ama haddii aan la haynin taariikhda cudur-darrada cad ee saddexda shay ee muujinta cudur-darrada ah:
Taariikhda cudurrada faafa: (1) Taariikhda safarka ama joogitaanka Magaalada Wuhan iyo aagagga ku hareereysan, ama bulshooyinka kale ee COVID-19 lagu soo sheegay 14 -kii maalmood ee ugu dambeeyay ka hor inta aanay calaamaduhu bilaaban; (2) Taariikhda la xiriirka xaaladaha faafa ee SARS - CoV-2 (oo leh tijaabinta nukliyeerka acid ee togan); (3) Taariikhda la xiriirka bukaanada qaba qandho ama astaamaha neefsashada ee ka imaanaya Magaalada Wuhan iyo aagagga ku hareereysan, ama bulshooyinka kale ee laga soo sheegay COVID-19 14kii maalmood ee ugu dambeeyay ka hor inta aanay calaamaduhu bilaaban; (4) Taariikhda la xiriirka kooxda la xaqiijiyay (≥ 2 xaaladaha qandhada iyo/ama 2 ka mid ah xaaladaha neefsashada ee ka dhacay aagagga yar sida guriga, xafiiska, fasalka dugsiga, iwm.)
Muuqaallada caafimaad: (1) qandho iyo/ama astaamaha neefsashada; (2) oo leh astaamo muujinaya caabuqa COVID-19; (3) wadarta unugyada dhiigga cad ee muujinaya caadi, hoos u dhac, ama unugyada dhiigga oo yaraada marxaladda hore.
Baaritaanka kiiska la xaqiijiyay waa inuu ku saleysnaadaa kiis laga shakiyay oo leh hal shay oo ah cudur ama cadeyn silikoon ah oo ah: (1) baaritaanka PCR ee waqtiga dhabta ah ee SARS-CoV-2 ayaa laga helay; (2) taxanaha hidda-wadaha fayraska oo dhan oo muujinaya isku midnimo sare leh oo la yaqaan coronavirus-ka cusub; (3) baaritaanka serum oo laga helay IgM antigen iyo IgG antigen gaar ah oo loogu talagalay SARS-CoV-2; ama IgG antigen gaar ah oo loogu talagalay SARS-CoV-2 oo laga beddelay diidmo-xumo, ama la kordhiyay ≥ 4 jeer marxaladda caafimaad ee aan la qabsan karin marka loo eego marxaladda degdegga ah ee soo noqoshada.
Waxaan arki karnaa in tijaabada PCR ee waqtiga dhabta ah ee nucleic acid ee nidaamka neefsashada ama shaybaarada dhiigga lagu daray qaybaha labaad (Jan. 18, 2020) iyo saddexaad (Jan. 22, 2020).
