Bishii Abriil 10, 2020, Google iyo Apple waxay si wada jir ah ugu dhawaaqeen inay si toos ah ugu dhex gali doonaan shaqeynta inay taageeraan barnaamijyada ku saleysan Bluetooth ee nidaamyadooda hawlgalka ee Android iyo iOS.
