Waa nidaam cilmi baaris cilmiyeed oo hadda la raacayo si loo horumariyo daaweyn COVID-19 oo aamin ah oo wax ku ool ah.
Tilmaamaha kale ee cilmi -baarista waxaa ka mid ah horumarinta tallaalka COVID-19 iyo gelinta plasma oo la xiriirta faa'iidooyinka caafimaad. SARS -CoV-2 wuxuu leeyahay ku dhawaad 66 borotiinno bartilmaameed ah, oo mid kasta uu leeyahay dhowr meelood oo ligand-ku xidhna.
Falanqaynta goobaha xidhitaanka waxay bixisaa mashruuc ku habboon horumarinta daawooyinka fayraska ee wax ku oolka ah ee ka hortaga COVID-19.
Kuwa ugu muhiimsan ee SARS-CoV-2 ay bartilmaameedsanayaan waa proteases-ka la midka ah ee loo yaqaan 'papen-like', RNA-dependent RNA polymerase, helicase, S protein, iyo ADP ribophosphate.
Hussain iyo kuwa kale waxay barteen dhowr isku-dhaf oo musharrax ah, ka dibna loo habeeyay lana falanqeeyay qaab dhismeedkooda si ay ula mid noqdaan daawooyinka la ansixiyay ee ugu badan ee la isku dhajiyo si loo dardar geliyo horumarinta daawo-ka-hortagga SARS-CoV-2 ee wax ku oolka ah ee daraasadda ka hortagga caafimaad ee lagu taliyay qaab dhismeedka daraasadda caafimaad.
Chloroquine waa daawo ka hortagta duumada, waxaa loo isticmaalaa in lagu difaaco cudurada is difaaca ee qaarkood.
On March 18, WHO ayaa ku dhawaaqday in Chloroquine iyo Hydroxychloroquine la xiriira ay ka mid noqon doonaan afarta daroogood ee lagu baranayo qayb ka mid ah tijaabada caafimaad ee Solidarity.
Guddoomiyaha New York Andrew Cuomo ayaa ku dhawaaqay in tijaabooyinka New York State ee Chloroquine iyo Hydroxychloroquine ay bilaaban doonaan 24-ka Maarso. 28-ka Maarso, FDA waxay oggolaatay isticmaalka Hydroxychloroquine Sulfate iyo Chloroquyl Phosphate iyada oo la raacayo Awoodda Isticmaalka Degdegga ah (EUA).
Daaweynta ma aysan ansixin FDA ee nidaamka tijaabada caafimaad waxayna u oggolaatay EUA kaliya daaweyn tijaabo ah oo loogu talagalay isticmaalka degdegga ah ee bukaanada isbitaalka ku jira laakiin aan awoodin inay daaweeyaan tijaabada caafimaad.
CDC waxay sheegtay in "Isticmaalka, qiyaasta ama muddada loo isticmaalo hydroxychloroquine ee ka hortagga ama daaweynta caabuqa SARS-CoV-2" aan weli la dejin.
