Sida laga soo xigtay South China Morning Post, Shinzo Abe wuxuu u diray maamulka Trump soo jeedin ku saabsan iibsashada daawada. Daawadan ayaa laga yaabaa inay waxtar yar u leedahay kiisaska daran ee cudurka, halkaasoo fayrasku horay usii badnaaday.
Waxaa laga yaabaa inaysan amaan ahayn in ay isticmaalaan dumarka uurka leh ama kuwa isku dayaya inay uur yeeshaan.
Daraasad la sameeyay oo la sameeyay oo la isku daray Lopinavir/Ritonavir (Calatra), oo ah daawada lidka ku ah fayraska loo yaqaan 'lopinavir' iyo 'ritonavir', ayaa la soo gabagabeeyay "wax faa'iido ah lama arag".
