Tijaabada labaad ee Angiotensin-converting enzyme 2 ayaa la wadaa in lagu qiimeeyo waxtarka daaweynta iyadoo la raacayo 200 bukaan oo ka imanaya xaalado xanuun oo halis ah, oo la dhigo isbitaalada Denmark, Jarmalka iyo Austria.
Baarayaasha Machadka Wadnaha ee Montreal ee Kanada ayaa hadda baranaya doorka colchicine ee yareynta caabuqa iyo dhibaatooyinka sambabka ee bukaannada qaba astaamaha fudud ee COVID-19.
