Tallaalka COVID-19 waa tallaal la soo jeediyay oo looga difaacayo cudurka coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Inkastoo aysan jirin tallaal dhameystiray tijaabooyinka caafimaad, haddana waxaa jira dadaalo badan oo lagu horumarinayo tallaalka noocan oo kale ah.
Dhamaadkii Febraayo 2020, Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO) ayaa sheegay inuusan filayn in talaal looga hortago SARS-CoV-2, fayraska keena cudurka, uu heli karo wax ka yar 18 bilood.
Shan tallaal oo tartamaya ayaa ku jiray marxaladda koowaad ee baaritaanka badbaadada bishii Abriil.
COVID-19 waxaa la aqoonsaday bishii Diseembar 2019.
Sanadkii 2020 waxaa jiray faafitaan weyn oo caalamka oo dhan ah, taas oo keentay in la maalgeliyo oo la baaro si loo helo tallaal.
Ururo badan ayaa isticmaalaya genomes-ka la daabacay si ay u horumariyaan talaal la filayo oo looga hortago SARS-CoV-2.
Sida lagu sheegay bishii Abriil, waxyaabaha lagama maarmaanka u ah hindisaha CEPI ee horumarinta tallaalka waa xawaare, awooda wax soo saarka, qorsheynta baaxada leh iyo helitaanka caalamiga ah.
Bishii Abriil, saynisyahannada CEPI waxay ku warrameen in 10 madal oo kala duwan oo tiknoolajiyad ah ay ku jireen cilmi baarista iyo horumarinta intii lagu jiray bilowgii 2020 si loo sameeyo tallaal wax ku ool ah oo ka ilaaliya COVID-19.
Barashada amaanka ee wajiga 1aad ee horumarsan hadafyada ugu muhiimsan ee layliska waxaa ka mid ah:
Nukliyeerka (DNA iyo RNA) (Qeybta I horumariyaha iyo Musharaxa tallaalka: Moderna, mRNA-1273)
Daawada fayraska (Qorshaha Horumarinta Wejiga 1aad iyo Musharaxa Tallaalka: CanSino Biologics, Adenovirus nooca 5da Daawada)
Sida ay ku warbixiyeen saynisyahannada CEPI bishii Abriil, 115 wadarta tallaalka murashaxa ayaa ku jira marxaladda horumarinta hore, kuwaas oo 78 lagu xaqiijiyay inay yihiin mashaariic firfircoon (sida uu sheegayo Machadka Milken 79), iyo 37 kale oo la shaaciyay, laakiin macluumaad dadweyne oo yar ayaa la heli karaa (waa la naqshadeeyay ama qorshaynayaa).
Tijaabada wajiga I-II waxay leedahay baaritaano badbaado iyo difaac ah oo horey loo sameeyay, sida caadiga ah waa la kala soocay, placebo-xakamayn iyo meelo badan, iyadoo la go'aaminayo qiyaasta saxda ah, ee wax ku oolka ah.
Tijaabada wajiga III caadi ahaan waxay ku lug leedahay dad badan, oo ay ku jiraan koox koontarool ah oo la kormeero saameynta xun ee qiyaasta ugu wanaagsan, iyo tijaabinta waxtarka tallaalka si looga hortago cudurka.
79 ka mid ah musharixiinta tallaalka ee horumarka firfircoon (oo la xaqiijiyay horraantii Abriil 2020), 74 weli kuma jirin qiimeynta aadanaha (wali waxay ku jireen cilmi baaris "hore").
24ka Janaayo 2020 gudaheeda Australia, Jaamacadda Queensland waxay ku dhawaaqday inay baarayaan suurtagalnimada tallaalka molikal-ka oo ay ku beddeli doonaan hidde-tallaalka borotiinka fayraska si uu u keeno jawaab-celin difaac.
Ku dhawaad 24 Janaayo 2020 gudaha Kanada, Xarunta Caalamiga ah ee Tallaalka (VIDO-InterVac) ee Jaamacadda Saskatchewan waxay ku dhawaaqday inay bilaabeen inay ka shaqeeyaan talaal, iyagoo ujeedkoodu yahay inay bilaabaan tijaabooyinka aadanaha 2021.
Mashruucyada horumarinta tallaalka waxaa lagu dhawaaqay Xarunta Xakamaynta iyo Kahortagga Cudurada ee Shiinaha 26 Janaayo 2020 iyo Jaamacadda Hong Kong 28 Janaayo.
Qiyaastii 29 Janaayo 2020, shirkadda dawooyinka ee Yansen oo uu hogaamiyo Haneke Schuetmaker ayaa ku dhawaaqday inay bilowday inay ka shaqeyso horumarinta tallaal.
Yansen wuxuu horumarinayaa tallaal afka ah isaga iyo wada -shaqeeyaha bayotechnoolajiyada ee Vaxart.
18 Maarso 2020, Emergent Biosolutions waxay ku dhawaaqday iskaashi wax soo saar si ay u horumariyaan tallaalka Vaccart.
8 Febraayo 2020, Oncogene Laboratory oo ku taal Romania ayaa daabacday warqad ku saabsan naqshadeynta tallaalka oo la mid ah farsamada loo adeegsado daaweynta tallaalka neoantigen ee kansarka.
25kii Maarso, madaxa machadka cilmi baarista ayaa ku dhawaaqay inay dhammaystireen isku darka tallaalka ayna bilaabayaan tijaabinta.
27 Febraayo 2020, NuGenerex Immuno-Oncology, oo ah shirkad ka mid ah shirkadaha Generex, ayaa ku dhawaaqday inay bilaabayaan mashruuc tallaal oo ah in la sameeyo tallaalka peptide-ka ee loo yaqaan 'Lay-Key peptide' si looga ilaaliyo COVID-19.
Waxay rabeen inay soo saaraan tallaalka musharaxa ah ee lagu tijaabin karo aadanaha "90 maalmood gudahood".
5tii Maarso 2020, Jaamacadda Washington ee St. Louis waxay ku dhawaaqday qorshayaasheeda ku aaddan horumarinta tallaalka.
Bishii Maarso 5, 2020, Ciidanka Mareykanka ee Fort Detrick ee Cilmi-baadhista Caafimaadka iyo Maaddada iyo Walter Reed ee Machadka Cilmi-baarista ee Western Maryland ee Silver Spring, labaduba waxay ku dhawaaqeen inay ka shaqeynayaan tallaal.
Qiyaastii Maarso 10, 2020, Ururka Xalinta Xalka Nolosha Degdega ah wuxuu ku dhawaaqay inuu ka qaybqaadanayo horumarinta iyo soo saarista tallaalka.
Wuxuu la shaqeyn doonaa shirkada Novavax Inc.
Wada -hawlgalayaashu waxay ku dhawaaqeen qorshayaal tijaabooyin hore iyo tijaabooyin tijaabo ah oo wajiga 1 ah oo la bilaabi doono bisha Luulyo 2020.
12-kii Maarso, 2020, Wasaaradda Caafimaadka ee Hindiya ayaa ku dhawaaqday inay la shaqaynayaan 11 shirkadood, iyo in ugu yaraan hal sano iyo bar ilaa laba sano ay qaadan doonto in la soo saaro tallaal, xitaa haddii ay degdeg tahay.
On 12 Maarso 2020 Medicago, oo ah shirkad tiknoolajiyad nololeed oo ku taal magaalada Quebec ee gobolka Quebec, ayaa soo warisay horumarka qayb ka mid ah walxaha la mid ah coronavirus-ka oo ay qayb ahaan maalgelin ka heleen Machadka Kanada ee Cilmi baarista Caafimaadka.
Duruusta ayaa ku jirta baaritaanka shaybaarka, tijaabinta bini aadamka ayaa la qorsheeyay in la sameeyo bisha July ama August 2020.
Horaantii toddobaadkaas, The Guardian ayaa soo warisay in Madaxweynaha Mareykanka Donald Trump uu u soo bandhigay Kurwaac "lacag aad u badan oo loogu talagalay helitaanka gaar ah ee tallaalka COVID-19", taas oo ay dowladda Jarmalka ka soo horjeesatay.
17 Maarso 2020, shirkadda dawooyinka ee Maraykanka ee Pfizer ayaa ku dhawaaqday inay iskaashi la sameysay shirkadda Jarmalka ee BioNTech si wadajir ah u horumariyaan tallaalka ku saleysan mRNA.
Daawada mRNA-ku saleysan ee BNT162 ayaa hada ku jirta tijaabinta hore ee bukaan-socodka, iyadoo tijaabooyinka bukaan-socodka la filayo inay bilaabmaan bisha Abriil 2020.
17kii Maarso 2020 gudaha Talyaaniga, shirkad Talyaani ah oo bioteknoolojiyad ah Tacis Biotech ayaa ku dhawaaqday inay heli doonaan natiijooyinka tijaabada ka hortagga bukaan socodka bisha Abriil 2020 iyo tijaabooyinka laga yaabo inay ku bilaabaan tallaalka ugu dambeeya ee tallaalka.
Faransiiska 19 Maarso 2020, Isbahaysiga Hal-abuurka Diyaargarowga Aafada (CEPI) ayaa ku dhawaaqay maalgashiga US $ 4.9 milyan oo ah ururka cilmi baarista tallaalka COVID-19, oo ay ku jiraan Institut Pasteur, Themis Bioscience (Vienna, Austria) iyo Jaamacadda Pittsburgh, taas oo ku daraysa maalgashiga CEPI ee US $ 29 milyan ee horumarinta tallaalka COVID-19.
Shirkadaha kale ee maalgashiga CEPI ee horumarinta tallaalka COVID-19 waa Moderna, Curevac, Inovio, Novavax, Jaamacadda Hong Kong, Jaamacadda Oxford, iyo Jaamacadda Queensland.
Bishii Maarso 20, 2020, saraakiisha caafimaadka ee Ruushka ayaa ku dhawaaqay in saynisyahannadu ay bilaabeen tijaabooyinka xayawaanka ee lix tallaal oo kala duwan.
Baarayaasha Imperial College London ayaa ku dhawaaqay 20-kii Maarso 2020 inay horumarinayaan tallaalka RNA ee iskiis u koray ee COVID-19.
Musharaxa tallaalkan waxaa la soo saaray 14 maalmood gudahood ka dib markii laga helay Shiinaha.
